  "name": "RPlog_When_Caspians_Attack_Part_2",
  "title": "The Fall of Ambassador Delgard",
  "summary": "As the New Republic Embassy in Plaxton City is overrun, Imperial storm-commandos breach the lobby and slaughter the last defending marines, then drive deeper to corner Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard in her quarters. Out of options, Ambrosia records a final defiant broadcast to New Republic command, demanding they recover her daughter Gabi and the Jedi and take them far away, before deactivating her hearing aids and making a last stand. She kills the commando who hot-wires her door and wounds another, but is ultimately felled by a stun bolt, cracking her skull on the marble floor. The commandos discover the captured naval prisoners, but an aristocratic voice from the orbiting Nemesis coldly orders that there be no survivors. With the embassy gutted and the marines dead, the commandos gather their casualties and the unconscious ambassador and commence extraction.",
